<br>
While Trak is an easier dragon himself, any guild that can clear to him and pull Prot has my vote as being able to kill Sev.  Sev has been upgraded (fyi).  He has Wuoshi's stun now, so you resist it less, and he can gate.  NB learned this the hard way, one cold October morning.  A gating dragon that stuns = a sick, sad joke.<br>
<br>
